{"tid":1871243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警上門查鰂魚涌夫婦爭吵案揭一家三口發燒 齊送院治療","createTime":"2020-02-09T10:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T10:40:55.000Z","uid":239336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"39d9ea8f093875857b2453d02a9b1b03dd9d1353","tid":1871243,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"妻子發燒，丈夫拒讓妻子進家門？昨晚約9時半，鰂魚涌英皇道1010至1026號海景樓一單位傳出爭呼聲，消息指一名43歲姓吳婦人，昨晚回家時，現時消息稱46歲姓王丈夫據報疑因擔心太太疑染武漢肺炎，一度拒絕她入屋返家，雙方激烈爭拗，吳婦一度報警求助。警到場調查後，相信事件無刑事成份，卻發現上址一家三口包括兩夫妻及15歲兒子俱身體不適及疑似發燒。為安全計遂召喚救護車，由穿上保護袍的消防員及救護員到場，把三人送往東區醫院作檢查及治療，案件列作糾紛案處理。<br />\n<br />\n記者今日重返事發現場，發現吳婦所住單位無人應門，有街坊則指今晨管理人員前來門外清潔消毒。不過有該大廈的消息人士堅稱，事件只是一場誤會，起因是有人昨晚喝了酒，溝通出現問題。<br />\n記者正向衞生署查詢事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200209/KRPITVWHYUCK4RVIJBYM4OSZSI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200209%2FKRPITVWHYUCK4RVIJBYM4OSZSI%2F&d=HBevYr6AXW9Qrc%2FJEBnfqi1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=65c83573\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200209%2FKRPITVWHYUCK4RVIJBYM4OSZSI%2F&h=6cac9f5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200209/KRPITVWHYUCK4RVIJBYM4OSZSI/</a><br />\n<br />\n黑警睇路<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f701841caf055d39e22ca920dea0dc2380c60a57","tid":1871243,"uid":321618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 p牌開post... <br />\n借個位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">上個月粉嶺PTU 16槍 懷疑槍決手足 </span><br />\n真相未明 無後續？<br />\n叫曬救命 點解要開槍？？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1871201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1871201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7d3442fefb540bff11f14d3103d1ba6b26f9efba","tid":1871243,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T10:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac3d73fe5ba8d9393e1df1126a88d6b7b7177cd","tid":1871243,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T10:38:40.000Z","msg":"熱烈地彈琴熱烈地唱"},{"pid":"d188919ca32b4fec699c0dd5ea73f230239042ff","tid":1871243,"uid":115214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T10:40:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}